### Political Leaders by Generational Type (Figure 12-8)

**DOMINANT GENERATIONS:**

- **IDEALISTS**: John Winthrop (MA), William Berkeley (VA), Samuel Adams, Benjamin Franklin, James Polk, Abraham Lincoln, Herbert Hoover, Franklin Roosevelt

- **CIVICS**: Gordon Saltonstall (CT), Robert "King" Carter (VA), Thomas Jefferson, James Madison, ——, ——, John Kennedy, Ronald Reagan

**RECESSIVE GENERATIONS:**

- **REACTIVES**: Nathaniel Bacon (VA), William Stoughton (MA), George Washington, John Adams, Ulysses Grant, Grover Cleveland, Harry Truman, Dwight Eisenhower

