- **Don't expect Social Security to help them** when old
- Like age 61.5, doubts about their future would require triggered political action
- **Inner-fixated Boomers**: negative expectation = "adjustment to karma," not great cause for alarm
- **No problem if Boom self-esteem remains unconquerable**
- **Old Aquarians** will consider themselves "together" people, sensing their physical mortality and susceptibility to **fourth dimension (time)**
- **Boomers will turn focus to the fifth dimension—the spiritual**
- Other generations will find this attitude peculiar, even frightening
- **Inner fixation allows graceful coping** without wasting resources on loftier community goals

### What Boomers Will Demand from the Young

