## Index of Names

### Index Structure and Conventions
- Index includes only **proper names of persons**
- Following each American name: generational membership indicated by abbreviation within parentheses
- **"?"** following abbreviation = unable to verify birthyear and generation exactly
- Following each foreign name: **locate nationality and generation** of American cohort born in same year
- Uses designational **"Reformation Cycle"** for birthyears between 1483 and 1583
- **"Medieval"** or **"Ancient"** for earlier birthyears

